		<path d="M10 8.5C8.7 6 5.8 3.4 4 3.4 2.6 3.4 2 4.5 2 5.9c0 1.4.8 4 1.3 4.7.7 1 2 1.2 3.2 1-1.2.2-2.3.6-1 2.1.9 1 1.9 0 2.4-1 .3-.5.5-1 1.1-1 .6 0 .8.5 1.1 1 .5 1 1.5 2 2.4 1 1.3-1.5.2-1.9-1-2.1 1.2.2 2.5 0 3.2-1 .5-.7 1.3-3.3 1.3-4.7 0-1.4-.6-2.5-2-2.5-1.8 0-4.7 2.6-6 5.1z"></path>
